title: Rush - A Desert Passage (Live Hemispheres Tour Bootleg 11-20-78)
description:
Soundboard recording of Rush live at the Tucscon Convention Center Arena in Tuscon, AZ on November 20, 1978 during their Hemispheres tour:

DISC 1:
Intro
Anthem
A Passage To Bangkok
By-Tor & The Snow Dog
Xanadu
Announcement
Something For Nothing
The Trees
Cygnus X-1
Hemispheres
Closer To The Heart

DISC 2:
Circumstances
A Farewell To Kings
La Villa Strangiato
2112 (Complete song except for V.Oracle:The Dream)
Working Man
Bastille Day
In The Mood
Drum Solo/Finale


Lineup:
Geddy Lee - vocals, bass, keyboards
Alex Lifeson - guitars
Neil Peart - drums and percussion
